# Per-package gitignore for @ever-works/ui.
#
# Most generic patterns (node_modules/, coverage/, dist/, test-results/,
# playwright-report/) are already covered by the repo-root .gitignore.
# This file adds package-specific exclusions only.
#
# Created in iteration 112 (2026-04-27) as a Phase 0 prerequisite
# of the Q22 follow-up #3 (`playwright-coverage` integration) plan
# at docs/plans/q22-playwright-coverage.md.

# Throwaway scratch dirs used by Phase 0 smoke tests.
# The plan creates `packages/ui/scratch/coverage-smoke/` to install
# `monocart-coverage-reports` against a one-off package.json so the
# library can be validated end-to-end before it pollutes the workspace
# pnpm-lock.yaml. The scratch dir is deleted at the end of Phase 0,
# but the gitignore entry remains so future smoke tests reuse the
# convention.
scratch/

# Coverage outputs.
# Already ignored by the repo-root .gitignore via the `coverage/` rule;
# duplicated here per Phase 1 step 3 of the playwright-coverage plan
# (`docs/plans/q22-playwright-coverage.md`) so the per-package contract
# is self-contained — running `pnpm --filter @ever-works/ui test:ct`
# against a checkout that lacks the root .gitignore (e.g. a published
# package extraction) still ignores the generated artifacts under
# `packages/ui/coverage/` (Vitest V8 output) and
# `packages/ui/coverage/ct/` (Playwright CT V8 output).
coverage/
